Best Paper Award &ldquo;1-Lipschitz Neural Distance Fields&rdquo;
Guillaume Coiffier and Louis Bethune
Best Paper Award: Runner up &ldquo;Cascading upper bounds for triangle soup Pompeiu-Hausdorff distance&rdquo;
Leonardo Sacht and Alec Jacobson
Best Paper Award: Runner up &ldquo;Integer-Sheet-Pump Quantization for Hexahedral Meshing&rdquo;
